Community number one,
I could write Simpson's

00:02:29.730 --> 00:02:31.300
Index of Diversity's going to be equal

00:02:31.300 --> 00:02:34.260
to one minus, and actually let me do

00:02:34.260 --> 00:02:36.610
the denominator right over here.

00:02:36.610 --> 00:02:38.090
What's the total population size?

00:02:38.090 --> 00:02:40.610
We have one, two, three, four, five, six,

00:02:40.610 --> 00:02:43.170
seven, eight, nine, 10, 11, 12.

00:02:43.170 --> 00:02:45.090
So capital N is 12.

00:02:45.090 --> 00:02:49.960
So we're gonna have 12 times
12 minus one, so 12 times 11.

00:02:49.960 --> 00:02:52.587
And then up here we're
going to first think about

00:02:52.587 --> 00:02:54.730
