00:02:54.730 --> 00:02:56.300
We could view that as our first species.

00:02:56.300 --> 00:02:59.950
So one, two, three,
four, five, six, seven.

00:02:59.950 --> 00:03:02.750
So we're gonna have seven
times seven minus one,

00:03:02.750 --> 00:03:04.380
so seven times six.

00:03:04.380 --> 00:03:06.820
Seven times six.

00:03:06.820 --> 00:03:10.130
And then to that we are going to add

00:03:10.130 --> 00:03:12.210
the population of our second species.

00:03:12.210 --> 00:03:13.860
One, two, three, four, five.

00:03:13.860 --> 00:03:16.410
So it's going to be five times one less

00:03:16.410 --> 00:03:18.200
