00:03:39.710 --> 00:03:41.360
I can get a calculator out for that.

00:03:41.360 --> 00:03:45.960
62 divided by 132 is equal to that.

00:03:45.960 --> 00:03:49.070
Put a negative sign on it
and then add it to one.

00:03:49.070 --> 00:03:54.070
So plus one is equal to 0.53.

